{"tid":1125331,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"可能係連登第一個Discord電台","createTime":"2019-04-25T15:25:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T14:57:46.000Z","uid":44132,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"626ac7ee73cc517b1217ec9ee78e8ec8a7fa74f7","tid":1125331,"uid":44132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:25:04.000Z","msg":"最近發現Discord原來有個bot可以一路播歌 一路傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁啱小弟喺外國身邊又無咩做 所以同幾個巴打開左個台 想睇下有無巴絲打同我地一樣無咩嘢做 又想搵嘢聽下 咪入黎傾下計吹下水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果巴絲打有心事感情學業工作煩惱都可以係度分享 睇下咁其他巴打有無咩意見畀到你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n得閒仲可以點下歌開心share大家音樂既興趣 無聊想廢up下都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最緊要係要禁入嚟睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家已經有超過「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">600</span></span>」個巴絲打入咗頻道啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開台時間大約係「<span style=\"color: red;\">2300-0200</span>」<br />\n<br />\n有興趣就入嚟聽聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲可以試下Call-In<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳送門: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/qFTfqpc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FqFTfqpc&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreGsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=238cdb2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/qFTfqpc</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「入咗台嘅巴絲打記住要開notification 方便追蹤本台最新消息」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ab203ac2ba1878ee3e4e95eea707ba1ba23859","tid":1125331,"uid":44132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4fc3a573e3f134b2556b7d510b244431d3f2a2","tid":1125331,"uid":180499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:44:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff9074be9e42dfe1eb7959037416a1cbb911e02","tid":1125331,"uid":44132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T12:03:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3322b670982e33d7fb7e667ab83aa928071633a2","tid":1125331,"uid":44132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T12:04:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dae37218486aa05d8d1ef116c17a010e03cdd6b","tid":1125331,"uid":44132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T13:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a955d078b18511d4f396259219e67416816378b6","tid":1125331,"uid":44132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc8414dcda6d65584cdd475fd18c75a03c75edc","tid":1125331,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dfe5379d25dec613b260874813837c03b3c6968","tid":1125331,"uid":136412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:38:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ede98e65334ff0e55aaf11e11